ailable data and of engineering and geological interpretation and judgment. Results of", "bbox": [85.5, 1483.5, 1157.8, 1506.5]}, {"text": "subsequent drilling, testing and production may cause either upward or downward revision of previous estimates. Further, the", "bbox": [85.5, 1508.5, 1157.8, 1531.5]}]}